<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recipe Book</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/recipeFrom.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Abril+Fatface&family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,100..900;1,9..144,100..900&family=Merriweather:ital,opsz,wght@0,18..144,300..900;1,18..144,300..900&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Quicksand:wght@300..700&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..60,200..900;1,8..60,200..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="recipeFromWrapper">
        <h1>Create</h1>
        <div class="recipeFromCol">
            

            <!-- Explanation Section 1: Convert Link -->
            <div class="explanation-box">
                <div class=explanation-title>
                    <img src="/imgs/convert.png">
                    <h2>Convert Recipes from Popular Sites</h2>
                </div>
                <p>Paste a link from a supported website, and we'll automatically import the recipe for you! </p>
                <p>Popular sites include: <a href="https://Allrecipes.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Allrecipes.com</a>, <a href="https://BudgetBytes.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BudgetBytes.com</a>, <a href="https://TamingTwins.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TamingTwins.com</a></p>
                <a href="/supportedSites">See all supported websites</a> <!-- Corrected href -->
                <a href="/convertRecipe">
                    <button class="recipeFrom">Convert Link to Recipe</button>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="explanationLesserRow">
                <!-- Explanation Section 2: Save Link -->
                <div class="explanation-box">
                    <div class=explanation-title>
                        <img src="/imgs/link.png">
                        <h2>Save a Recipe Link</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>Found a recipe on an unsupported site or just want to keep the original link handy? Save it directly here.</p>
                    <a href="/newRecipeLink">
                        <button class="recipeFrom">Save Recipe Link</button>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Explanation Section 3: Handtyped -->
                <div class="explanation-box">
                    <div class=explanation-title>
                        <img src="/imgs/add.png">
                        <h2>Add a Manual Recipe</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>Need to archive one of grandma's old recipes? Immortalize it here by typing it out yourself.</p>
                    <a href="/newRecipePage">
                        <button class="recipeFrom">Add Manual Recipe</button>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Explanation Section 4: Picture -->
                <div class="explanation-box">
                    <div class=explanation-title>
                        <img src="/imgs/photo.png">
                        <h2>Upload a Recipe Photo</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>Took a cheeky picture of a recipe book in the grocery store? We won't tell. Upload the image here.</p>
                    <a href="/newRecipePicture">
                        <button class="recipeFrom">Upload Recipe Photo</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
